section_data.description: Angelic, bulb holding cherubs, Greek gods performing millennial activities, great men across history photoshopped to fit into the current generation--Daddy offers a plethora of kitschy decor. The rooftop is an antithesis to the circus below: al fresco dining, with simple seating, a row of curtained cabanas on one end and an island bar; the vast, blue sky is the main attraction here. The latest addition to 12th Main Indiranagar, Daddy clearly offers the best of both worlds, with the contrasting ambience and its multi-cuisine menu.
